{
  "chapter": 60,
  "chapter_summary": "第六十回 该下地狱的时候\n\n班察巴那向小方展示一张薄羊皮地图，标出吕三一百九十一个秘密巢穴。两人讨论如何找到吕三——人力不足以分头搜寻，且吕三戒备森严。班察巴那提出诱敌之计：放出消息让吕三知道秘图已被掌握，吕三必然调集高手加强戒备，由此暴露行踪。班察巴那坦白此行极险，只能让小方去执行。小方淡然接受。\n\n场景转至吕三的黄金密室。吕三独坐纯金铸就的屋中饮酒，亲信苗宣闯入报告班察巴那的行动计划。吕三不动声色，先问苗宣跟随自己多久（精确到月日），再指出苗宣违反了两条命令：擅闯禁室、拒绝陪酒。吕三以公正为名逼苗宣自尽。苗宣想到妻儿，含泪自刺心脏而死。\n\n吕三随即召来另一亲信沙平。沙平与苗宣截然不同——谨慎低调，从不违令。吕三问是否应调集人手，沙平指出班察巴那尚不知吕三所在，调集人手反而暴露位置。两人以一问一答的方式，暗示下一步将采取更为隐蔽的应对策略。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这是玉门关内外，包括戈壁、拉萨圣峰都在内的一张地图。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这地区之大，广及五万五千里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是在这广大的地域中，有人烟的地方并不太多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你数一数，这张图上用朱砂笔点过的地方一共有多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "一共一百九十一处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这一百九十一个地方，都是吕三的秘密巢穴所在地。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "到目前为止，我们虽然只查出这么多，可是我相信他就算还有其他分舵、秘穴、暗卡，也不会太多了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "我也相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在我们一定要找到吕三。无论什么事都一定要找到他才能解决。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我相信我们一定可以在这些地方找到他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "你知不知道他究竟在哪一个分舵秘穴里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不知道。没有人知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们虽然早就查出了吕三的窝在些什么地方，可是我们一直都没有动手去找。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为我们知道找不到他的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们没有这么多的人力，可以分成一百九十一队人，分头去找。就算我们能分出来，力量必定也已很薄弱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "吕三的行踪所在之地，警卫戒备一定极森严。就算我们有人能找到他，也不是他们的对手。如果我们一击不中，再想找他就更难了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "完全正确！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以我们绝不可轻举妄动，绝不能打草惊蛇。我们绝不能做没有把握的事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "现在你已经有把握？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在我至少已经想出了一个对付他的法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在我们虽然还是一样找不到他，但却可以要他自己把自己的行踪暴露出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "你真的有把握能做到？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你想不想听听我的计划？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "我想。非常想！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "第一，我们一定要先放出消息，让吕三知道我们已经查出了他一百九十一个秘密藏身处。我们甚至不妨将这张秘图公开，让他确信我们已经有了这种实力。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "第二呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "经过了这次挫败之后，他对我们绝不会再存轻敌之心了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "我相信他从来都没有轻视过你。谁也不敢轻视你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以他知道我们已经开始准备有所行动之后，一定会严加戒备。不管他在哪里，一定会立刻调集他属下的高手到那里去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "只要他一开始调动他属下的高手，我们就可以查出他在什么地方了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是的！我的计划就是这样子的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "只不过这项行动仍然很冒险。吕三财雄势大，属下高手如云，我们还是没有必胜的把握。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "但是这次机会我们绝不可错过。也许这已经是我们最后一次机会了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "我明白。所以我们就算明知要下地狱，也非去不可！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "可是你不能去。你还有别的事要做，你不能冒这种险！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是的。所以我只有让你去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "如果我们两个人之间一定有一个人要死，我也只有让你去死。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "好！我去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "你知不知道我最大的长处是哪一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "我最大的长处就是公正。我不能不公正。跟着我做事的人最少时也有八九千个，如果我不是公正，怎么能服得住人？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "你还记不记得刚才我进来时说过什么话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "苗宣",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "你说，任何人都不许走进这屋子的门，不管什么人都一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "你是不是人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "苗宣",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "现在你是不是已经进来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "苗宣",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我不一样。我有要紧的事。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "我只问你，现在你是不是已经进来了？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "苗宣",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "刚才我有没有叫你坐下来陪我喝杯酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "苗宣",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "你有没有坐下来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "苗宣",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "没有！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "你有没有陪我喝酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "苗宣",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "没有！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "你还记不记得我曾经说过的，我说出来的话就是命令？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "苗宣",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我记得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "那么你当然也应该记得，违背我命令的人应该怎么办？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "你跟我做事已经有多久了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "苗宣",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "十年。整整十年了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "不对。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "苗宣",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "不对？什么地方不对？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "不是十年。是九年十一个月，要到下个月的十三才满十年。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_miao_xuan",
      "text": "不管怎么样，你跟着我的时候已经不算太短了。已经应该看得出我是个什么样的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "苗宣",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我多少总能看得出一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "沙平。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "沙平在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "你知不知道班察巴那已下令要来攻击我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "你知不知道我们现在应该怎么做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "现在我们是不是应该将人手都调集到这里来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "不应该。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "因为班察巴那现在还不知道你在哪里。如果我们不告诉他，他永远都不会知道的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "如果我们这么样做，就等于已经告诉他了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_sha_ping",
      "text": "你既然明白这一点，就应该知道我们现在应该怎么样做了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_ping",
      "speaker_name": "沙平",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我不知道，我想过，可是我不知道要怎么样做才是对的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    }
